19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
20 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 47 O.S. 2021, Section 11-403.1, is
21 amended to read as follows:
22 Section 11-403.1. A. Any person convicted of failure to yield
23 a right-of-way and who causes a fatality or serious great bodily
24 injury, as defined in Section 11-904 of this title, as a result of
